title: Clown World Confessions Part I
author: VD
content_html:
Tonight we’re doing a UATV-exclusive reaction video to a former Clown World player’s perspective on the true development of the war between NATO and Russia. We should get rolling around 7 PM Eastern, so join us for the deep dive.
